abstract.4: born and raised in the borough of queens<Queens> in new york city<New_York_city>, university of pennsylvania<University_of_Pennsylvania>0 received a bachelor's degree in economics from the wharton school of the university of pennsylvania<University_of_Pennsylvania> in 1968
